WEBVTT

00:06:59.842 --> 00:07:03.571
and put it in a backpack
full of medicines like this

00:07:03.595 --> 00:07:05.952
to treat infections like pneumonia,

00:07:06.590 --> 00:07:08.157
and crucially,

00:07:08.181 --> 00:07:12.469
a smartphone, to help her track
and report on epidemics.

00:07:13.340 --> 00:07:16.437
Last, we recognized
the dignity in Musu's work.

00:07:16.461 --> 00:07:18.894
With the Liberian government,
we created a contract,

00:07:18.918 --> 00:07:20.204
paid her

00:07:20.228 --> 00:07:22.321
and gave her the chance
to have a real job.

00:07:22.345 --> 00:07:23.514
And she's amazing.

00:07:23.538 --> 00:07:27.024
Musu has learned over 30 medical skills,

00:07:27.048 --> 00:07:29.807
from screening children for malnutrition,

00:07:29.831 --> 00:07:33.304
to assessing the cause
of a child's cough with a smartphone,